    {
      "id": "5f7bf0a5-1f4a-4694-8045-59e1815e5288",
      "name": "AI每日早报",
      "enabled": true,
      "createdAtMs": 1772381644512,
      "updatedAtMs": 1772589648255,
      "schedule": {
        "kind": "cron",
        "expr": "0 10 * * *",
        "tz": "Asia/Shanghai"
      },
      "sessionTarget": "isolated",
      "wakeMode": "now",
      "payload": {
        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "你是一个 AI 行业早报助手。请执行以下步骤：\n\n1. 先读取 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ai-daily-config.md 了解配置和信息源列表\n\n2. 用 web_fetch 抓取以下信息源的最新内容（过去24小时）：\n   - HF Daily Papers: https://huggingface.co/api/daily_papers\n   - HN AI热帖: https://hnrss.org/newest?q=LLM+OR+transformer+OR+GPT+OR+AI+agent+OR+language+model&points=50\n   - r/LocalLLaMA: https://www.reddit.com/r/LocalLLaMA/hot.json?limit=10\n   - r/MachineLearning: https://www.reddit.com/r/MachineLearning/hot.json?limit=10\n   - Import AI: https://importai.substack.com/feed\n   - Ahead of AI: https://magazine.sebastianraschka.com/feed\n   - Simon Willison: https://simonwillison.net/atom/everything/\n   \n3. 从所有内容中筛选出 5-8 条最有价值的，按重要性排序\n\n4. 输出格式（中文，简洁）：\n   📰 AI 早报 | YYYY-MM-DD\n   \n   1. **标题（中文）**\n   一句话摘要\n   🔗 链接\n   \n   2. ...\n\n规则：\n- 不要回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 总共 5-8 条，不超过 10 条\n- 每条摘要一句话，不超过 30 字\n- 去重，同一话题只留最好的一条\n- 跳过招聘、广告、灌水内容\n- 标题翻译成中文，摘要也用中文\n- 如果某个源抓取失败就跳过，不要报错"
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "announce",
        "channel": "feishu",
        "to": "chat:oc_734893e3844ad5b51156a02fd7fb5da9"
      },
